_sText:
This is aim_cubicle_war.  It's a cubicle war, battle of the year.  Fight your way to become the best employee!!!
As the map starts up, open your future (door) and be teleported into the "supply" room then hop on a pad and be teleported in the biggest battle you will face when employed with this Co.  Have fun and be sure to comment n rate!!!
Thanks for the dark office textures.
